# Gameboard
@davcs86's gameboard demo.

## Stack

### Back-end

- Asp.Net Core 1.0.1 (MVC + Web API)
- [NoDb](https://github.com/joeaudette/NoDb) for data persistence.

### Front-end

- Angular 1.5 (Angular-UI, UI-Grid, Angular-Schema-Form) with ES6,
- SASS (Bootstrap-sass),
- Webpack 2 as module bundler.
- Gulp as Task Runner

### Testing

- xUnit,
- Moq

